<td colspan="3" align="center"><a href="/wiki/File:SATA_Slimline_Powercable.jpg" class="image" title="A 6-pin Slimline Serial ATA power connector."><img alt="A 6-pin Slimline Serial ATA power connector." src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4f/SATA_Slimline_Powercable.jpg/200px-SATA_Slimline_Powercable.jpg" width="200" height="152" border="0" /></a></td>
